	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>You fool! Do you know what you have done to my shop?? The world will long lament your heinous crime!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_DEFEATED_2">
			<Text>Curse you! The blood of the greatest leader in world history is on your hands!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_DEFEATED_3">
			<Text>You have defeated me?? But how could this have happened? There must be some mistake!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_ANOTHER_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>Your expansion efforts are an insult. Know that there will be consequences for this.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Ah, a new customer. Welcome. Do feel free to consult me if you become overwhelmed with the responsibilities of leadership.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_FIRSTGREETING_2">
			<Text>I graciously greet you, and generously offer you my hand in friendship and happiness. May our relationship is long-lasting in harmonious condition.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_FIRSTGREETING_3">
			<Text>Welcome, Stranger to my Dive Shop! I am the best Dive Therapist out there. But of course you knew that.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Aghh, what do you want?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Welcome!!.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Hello friend. What brings you to my shop this day?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_ANOTHER_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>I see your armies amassed near my empire. If you wish to attack then come. Don't hide in the shadows like a child.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>You have a Luxury Resource that I would like to use for my shop. What do you think of this offer?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>I believe it's in our mutual interest to allow free passage between our two great empires.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_LUCA_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1">
			<Text>Unfortunately, my shop is currently experiencing some problems. Will you help me, please?</Text>
		</Row>
